<h2>Detailed Description</h2><div>This class is a convenient container for dealing with several threads at the same time.<br /> Performance Tip: If the threads within this container are destined to die, you should use the method stop() before destroying this class. This method will make them stop gracefully and asynchronously and you should earn a lot of time.<br /></div>
